1. *Glavi* se oko njega i traži odgovor. (She was pacing around him and searching for an answer.)
2. Ona ga je gledala i iznenađeno pogledala u *glavu* (She looked at him and then looked at his head in surprise.) 
3. On se okrenuo i pogledao u *glavu* ogromne skulpture. (He turned and looked at the head of the giant sculpture.)
4. On je lupio *glavom* o zid. (He was banging his head against the wall.) 
5. On je duboko uzdahnuo i zagledao se u *glavu* svog sina. (He sighed deeply and looked into the head of his son.)